        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks ACR for paper and comments on it ["On the denudation of South Wales", <hi rend="italic">Mem. Geol. Surv. G. B.</hi> 1 (1846): 297–335].</p>  
<p>Sends copy of <hi rend="italic">South America</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Discusses action of the sea.</p>
            <p>Criticises ACR’s views on sudden elevation of mountain chains.</p>
        </abstract>
